About
=====

This repository is designed to facilitate visualisations of New Zealand's coal
mining industry. Everything from their original sources have been cleaned up. 
You should be able to import the .tsv files into any computer software and begin
your analysis.


Contact
=======

My details are:

   Tim McNamara <paperless@timmcnamara.co.nz>
   @timClicks


Source
======

The source of the original files is Crown Minerals' website[1].


